text: Mouhamed Coly (born 13 September 1983 in Paris) is a French footballer. ==Career== Coly played previously for Dulwich Hamlet F.C. & Altrincham FC . ==References== ==External links== http://www.dulwichhamletfc.co.uk/news- story.php?ID=286 http://www.altrinchamfc.co.uk/110201wm.htm Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Senegalese footballers Category:Senegalese expatriate footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Sportspeople from Dakar
